{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "呃！？沙、沙音……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "啊……埃、埃尔菲莉丝。不是的。\\n我……我不是故意的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝，你醒醒啊！\\n啊、啊啊啊……\\n哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "对朋友也能毫不犹豫地痛下杀手，\\n你果然是猛兽呢，沙音。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "多萝西！这……这就是\\n你嫁祸给我的理由吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "先引起埃尔菲莉斯的疑心，\\n然后唆使她来跟我战斗，\\n只为借我的手杀死埃尔菲莉丝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "不仅如此，我还想让你意识到\\n你真正的归宿是我们这边——\\n暗杀的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你这个混蛋！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "我知道你很气愤，\\n但事实上正是你亲手杀掉了朋友，\\n我不过是为你准备这个舞台罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "这是无可动摇的事实。\\n今后你还能用那双杀害朋友的手\\n去抚摸孩子们的头吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "没错，你那把杀死朋友的利刃，\\n就为这个世界所用吧。只有这样，\\n你那圣天骑士朋友才能安息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你是……玛努古斯大主教。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "多亏了你，我才能得到炼狱之匙。\\n这样一来我就可以\\n为信徒们带来安宁了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "竟然说信徒们的安宁……\\n你不是为了与保守派融合\\n才这么做的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "一开始的确如此，但后来我发现\\n保守派无法摆脱现有价值观的桎梏，\\n开导他们只是浪费时间。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "所以我就换了一种方式。\\n我要将真相公之于众，\\n从根本上摧毁他们的价值观。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "为此才要把埃尔菲莉丝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "这一切都是为了真正的融合。\\n但就算真相摆在眼前，还是会有人\\n无法舍弃原有的价值观吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "那种蠢货毫无用处。\\n所以我需要有人来清理他们。\\n没错——需要你这样的暗杀者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "这里就是你的归宿，\\n回来我们身边吧，我的挚友。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉斯曾两次为我指明\\n前进的道路……圣城的伙伴们\\n帮助我开始了全新的人生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "即使背负着沾满鲜血的过去，我也要\\n和他们一同走上阳光明媚的道路。\\n这就是我的生存之道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "我很失望……没想到你竟然\\n如此胸无大志。看来不用再期待\\n你那光彩照人的样子了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "多萝西女官，我有一个新的委托。\\n那个蠢货对于真正的融合毫无用处。\\n请你立刻解决掉她。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "收到♪你也听到啦，\\n给我倒在鲜红的血泊里吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "呃！？这一击……力道好强劲！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "说起来这是我们第一次交战吧？\\n因为我擅长以智谋取胜\\n你就认为我很弱？真遗憾呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "啊哈哈哈哈哈♪啊哈哈哈哈哈♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "你是还没从刚才的战斗中\\n恢复过来吧？哎呀，我还以为\\n能再多享受一下乐趣呢～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "的确……现在的我\\n要对付你是很困难……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "即便如此我还是能赢。\\n两个人联手的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "什么！？你是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "圣、圣天骑士！？你怎么还活着！？\\n你不是死在沙音的利刃下了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "那是为了把你引出来\\n而合伙上演的一出戏呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我一来到这里，就确信沙音是无辜的。\\n之后我意识到向我提供情报的你\\n是一个暗杀者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "所以为了让在这个大圣堂里\\n静观事态发展的你放松警惕，\\n我就顺水推舟地假装被你骗了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我很快就明白过来，\\n埃尔菲莉斯是相信我的。\\n刀剑相向不过是演戏的一环。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "所以你们就即兴地演了一场戏！？\\n光凭那种暧昧模糊的交流，\\n对方怎么可能会懂！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "就算暧昧模糊也能懂。\\n因为我们是朋友啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "我竟然被人骗了？而且还是\\n被两个嘴上扯着什么友情的家伙？\\n怎么可能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "不可能，不可能，不可能！\\n只能由我来嘲笑别人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "开什么玩笑啊！\\n你们这些渣滓！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "呃！可、可恶……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "竟然是烟雾弹！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "今天就先放你们一马！\\n但这事儿还没完！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "多萝西",
            "context": "我发誓！我发誓一定要\\n彻底摧毁你们那所谓的友情，\\n把你们打入绝望的深渊中！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "啧！又让她跑了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "别去追她了，\\n现在我们该做的是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我们已经知道了你的阴谋。\\n你就乖乖接受公正的裁决吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "我就暂且服软吧……\\n但我是不会死心的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "玛努古斯大主教",
            "context": "因为我才是\\n伟大意志的执行者……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "业火之格里塞布尔姆事件\\n二十六天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "给，大姐姐。\\n这花送给你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "呵呵，谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我已经回来了啊……\\n回到了我所期望的日常之中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "不用担心，\\n你的嫌疑已经都洗清了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "可是大主教提到过的炼狱之匙\\n到底是什么？这跟他想要我的性命\\n有什么联系吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "谁知道呢……说起来，\\n我也有一件在意的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "为什么我们一见面，\\n你就确信了我是无辜的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "因为你的斗篷依旧洁白无垢啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你说过“白色的斗篷，是我发誓\\n不再沾染他人鲜血的证明”对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "呵呵……嗯，我的确说过呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "少女",
            "context": "大姐姐，\\n那边有更好看的花儿哦。\\n我们一起去采吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "嗯，好啊。那我们来比一比\\n谁先跑到那边吧？预备，跑！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "愿这份幸福，\\n能永远延续下去……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "沙音大人，\\n抱歉在您出游的时候前来打扰。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你是那时追捕我的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "我是来为我那时的无礼道歉的。\\n此外我还有一事相报。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "正在接受审问的\\n玛努古斯前大主教他……\\n自尽了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "自尽？你确定？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "监狱是密室，地上还插着一把刀。\\n一定是自杀不会错的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "本打算从他嘴里问出\\n那什么炼狱之匙的事，\\n这下真相就石沉大海了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "他是被灭口了……\\n从手法来看应该是“老师”干的吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "您说什么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "不，没什么。\\n这件事我会转告埃尔菲莉丝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "前图书管理员说过……\\n只要还有人想得到炼狱文书的续篇，\\n埃尔菲莉丝就会不断被追杀。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "但是，就算前方\\n是布满荆棘的路……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "喂，沙音！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我也一定会保护好\\n最重要的朋友！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100005_02_04_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}